    • Method Detail

      • callService

        public static org.apache.axiom.om.OMElement callService(java.lang.String enpointUri,
                                        java.lang.String soapAction,
                                        java.lang.String targetNamspace,
                                        java.lang.String method,
                                        java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object> paramsAndValuesMap)
                                                 throws java.lang.Exception
        Call a web service method and return OMElement.
        Parameters:
        enpointUri - is WSDL address.
        soapAction - is soapAction in WSDL document.
        targetNamspace - is targetNamespace attribute in tag root of WSDL document.
        method - is name of method (action) to call web service.
        paramsAndValuesMap - is list of parameters of method store in Map<String, Object> with parameter name is key (String) and value is an object (recommended String).
        Returns:
        OMElement contain result when execute web service successfully, otherwise return null.
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - contain a message to notice.
